SYSTEM MODIFICATION DISCLAIMER
===============================

This software modifies Windows Registry values, system services, power
configurations, and file system contents. While every effort has been made
to ensure safety (including automatic backup, restore points, and
confirmation prompts), the author:

1. Makes NO guarantees that any modification will improve system performance.
2. Is NOT responsible for any system instability, data loss, hardware
   damage, or any other consequence resulting from the use of this software.
3. STRONGLY recommends creating a System Restore Point before applying
   any tweaks (the software offers this at startup).
4. STRONGLY recommends running the software only on systems you own and
   are authorized to modify.

